C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/S%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-034/poem-fLLlubzzBDE4qUeKxfx5PA">Sơn cư bách vịnh kỳ 034 - 山居百詠其三十四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-jnvtlp5PrNS3FoOBBGt7-w">Tông Bản thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/T%E1%BA%BF-Tr%C3%ACnh-th%E1%BB%8B-mu%E1%BB%99i-V%C4%83n/poem-XjBLu2BujbX1LVfj9CLuSA">Tế Trình thị muội Văn - 祭程氏妹文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BA%A3o-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-wwxs7iJe3IRK6mSsXfh_gQ">Thảo đường - 草堂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tr%E1%BB%AB-th%E1%BA%A3o/poem-xZ1BB9vkb6BZXgwohAcJ2A">Trừ thảo - 除草</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
